description: The api tokenizes the expression text and create a tree model from the tokens.  Using the model, it can evaluate the expression or convert it to a expression of different format.  Some applications revert the process by creating the model first and using it to generate certain expression such as a sql query statement.  The api also contains a useful ExecutionContext class that allows evaluation of expressions with variables.  The variables can be read internally or directly from external objects.
summary: Albatross.Expression api is created to process and evaluate text based expression strings.
